tabind:2.22.0`.\n\nChanged files:\n- `tests/src/com.fasterxml.jackson.core/jackson-databind/2.22.0/src/test/java/com_fasterxml_jackson_core/jackson_databind/JacksonAnnotatedMethodTest.java`\n  - Replaced the Native Image failing JDK serialization path for `AnnotatedMethod` with metadata assertions that still exercise resolved `AnnotatedMethod` behavior.\n\n- `tests/src/com.fasterxml.jackson.core/jackson-databind/2.22.0/src/test/java/com_fasterxml_jackson_core/jackson_databind/JacksonConstructorPropertiesTest.java`\n  - Made the test class and constructor-property target type/constructor/getter public so Jackson can access the supported creator path under Native Image.\n\n- `tests/src/com.fasterxml.jackson.core/jackson-databind/2.22.0/src/test/java/com_fasterxml_jackson_core/jackson_databind/JacksonNamingStrategyTest.java`\n  - Made the top-level test class public.\n  - Added a `HandlerInstantiator` that supplies Jackson’s standard naming strategy singleton instances, preserving `@JsonNaming` coverage while avoiding unsupported reflective construction of strategy classes in Native Image.\n\n- `tests/src/com.fasterxml.jackson.core/jackson-databind/2.22.0/src/test/java/com_fasterxml_jackson_core/jackson_databind/JacksonOptionalSerializersTest.java`\n  - Made the top-level test class public.\n  - Registered the same optional SQL/XML/DOM serializers and deserializers explicitly through a `SimpleModule`, preserving functional serialization/deserialization coverage without relying on runtime `Class.forName` lookups for optional handler classes.\n\nNo metadata or Native Image config files were modified. Tests were not run, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00be1bf622941a28016a23436494f08190ba49d521f1cf5155\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 766, "output": 893, "cacheRead": 71680, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 73339, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead"